text: Obvinsk () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Obvinskoye Rural Settlement, Karagaysky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 583 as of 2010. There are 21 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km north from Karagay. == References == Category:Rural localities in Karagaysky District
title: Obvinsk
